         <abstract>
            <p>We derive a truncation error bound for limit periodic continued fractions $K(a_n/1)$ which, at least asymptotically, is best possible by comparison with periodic continued fractions. For a given limit periodic continued fraction the bound is easy to compute.</p>
          </abstract>
